Globaltrans of Russia Set for Biggest Gain in 4 Months on Profit

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-08-30T09:29:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-30/globaltrans-of-russia-set-for-biggest-gain-in-4-months-on-profit.html
Globaltrans Investment Plc (GLTR) ’s global
depositary receipts headed for the biggest gain since April
after  Russia ’s biggest non-state rail operator said first-half
profit increased 66 percent to $159 million from a year earlier
as economic recovery spurred demand.  The London-listed shares leapt 7.4 percent to $14.50 by
9:56 a.m., headed for the largest advance on a closing basis
since April 20.  To contact the reporter on this story:
